SQL_STMT_U.val: select cmon_clntno , cast ( sum(CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN + CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO) as decimal ( 13,2)) , cast ( sum( CMON_TOTIFACTCOMMSCHED +CMON_TOTIFACTCOMMSCHEDADD +CMON_TOTIMINCOMM+CMON_TOTIFIXCOMM) as decimal (13,2)) , cast ( sum(CMON_TOTIIFACTDEBIT+CMON_TOTIIFACTSURCHARGEOD+ CMON_TOTIIARRANGEM+CMON_TOTIISTOCK) as decimal ( 13,2)) from :1/cmon where cmon_year=:2 and cmon_admno=1 and cmon_clntno<99999 and cmon_currency='PLN' group by cmon_clntno;
